      <description>Even after deleting photos, storage remains full because they often move to a &amp;lsquo;Recently Deleted&amp;rsquo; folder for 30 days, plus caches and other hidden files take up space. To free up storage, permanently delete from Recently Deleted, clear app caches, and check for large files.</description>
